'''Tolstoy''' is a [[crap|popular]], disgusting, and untalented [[Inflation art|fat furry artist]] who is pretty much worshipped by every fucking [[faggot|fat furry]] on the [[internets]]. He is also the self-proclaimed "leader of the [[LOL WUT|Severe Duty Slobs]]", and has an imaginary clan of e-warriors called the [[Juggalo|Anla Shok]]. His sheer mass of fat and fail may soon grow beyond that of the critical mass, and will [[lhc|consume the earth in a massive wave of imploding gravity.]]


